    <!-- AmetCoin Overview Section -->
    <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>AmetCoin Overview</h2>
        <p>AmetCoin is a cutting-edge cryptocurrency designed to revolutionize digital transactions with enhanced security, scalability, and user-friendliness. Our blockchain-based platform aims to provide a seamless experience for both individual users and businesses.</p>
        
        <h3>What It Is</h3>
        <p>AmetCoin is a decentralized digital currency that operates on a secure blockchain network. Unlike traditional currencies, AmetCoin is not controlled by any central authority, making it resistant to government interference and inflation.</p>
        
        <h3>Purpose</h3>
        <p>The primary purpose of AmetCoin is to facilitate fast, secure, and low-cost transactions while providing a robust infrastructure for developers to build decentralized applications (dApps).</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Key Features and Benefits Section -->
    <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>Key Features and Benefits</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Enhanced Security:</strong> Advanced cryptographic protocols protect all transactions</li>
            <li><strong>Scalability:</strong> High transaction throughput to support growing user demand</li>
            <li><strong>Low Transaction Fees:</strong> Minimal costs for sending and receiving AmetCoin</li>
            <li><strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong> Intuitive design for both beginners and experienced users</li>
            <li><strong>Decentralized Governance:</strong> Community-driven decision-making process</li>
            <li><strong>Smart Contract Integration:</strong> Support for automated contract execution</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <!-- How to Get Started Section -->
    <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>How to Get Started</h2>
        <h3>Wallet Setup</h3>
        <p>To start using AmetCoin, you'll need a digital wallet. We recommend using our official wallet application or trusted third-party wallets that support AmetCoin.</p>
        
        <h3>Purchasing Options</h3>
        <p>You can purchase AmetCoin through various exchanges and platforms. Visit our official website for a list of supported exchanges and trading pairs.</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Technical Specifications Section -->
    <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>Technical Specifications</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Blockchain Type:</strong> Proof-of-Stake (PoS)</li>
            <li><strong>Consensus Mechanism:</strong> Delegated Proof-of-Stake (DPoS)</li>
            <li><strong>Block Time:</strong> Approximately 10 seconds</li>
            <li><strong>Transaction Speed:</strong> Up to 10,000 transactions per second</li>
            <li><strong>Supply Limit:</strong> 21 million coins</li>
            <li><strong>Network Security:</strong> Multi-layered security protocols</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Team/Developers Information Section -->
    <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>Team & Developers</h2>
        <p>AmetCoin is developed by a team of passionate engineers, cryptographers, and blockchain experts dedicated to creating the future of digital currency.</p>
        <p>Our core team includes specialists in distributed systems, cybersecurity, and financial technology. We also collaborate with a global community of developers and researchers.</p>
    </div>
    
